    | IOT_SENSOR_DATA
    | COMPUTATION_RESULT
    | CROSS_CHAIN_DATA
    | IDENTITY_DATA

Type AggregationMethod is:
    | MEDIAN
    | MEAN_WEIGHTED
    | VOLUME_WEIGHTED
    | REPUTATION_WEIGHTED
    | OUTLIER_FILTERED_MEDIAN
    | CONSENSUS_BASED

Type called "DataValue":
