        feed as None
        message as message

Process called "create_feed_success" that takes feed_id as String and feed as DataFeed returns FeedCreationResult:
    Return FeedCreationResult with:
        success as true
        feed_id as feed_id
        feed as feed
        message as "Data feed created successfully"

